<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3907606>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Anoplodactylus eroticus Stock, 1968 (P18–B0911SL6–01) male, a. trunk, dorsal view; b. trunk, lateral view; c. trunk, ventral view; d. ventrally spurs on the second coxae of leg 2 and 3; e. tarsus, propodus and claw of leg 2, arrows indicating the sole spines; f. tarsus, propodus and claw of leg 3, arrows indicating the sole spines. Scale bars a, b=1 mm, c, d =0.5 mm, e, f=0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3907606/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

